# Phase 2 — Make payments production-safe

**Goal: 7.2 → 8/10**
**Priority: required before charging real customers**

## 5. Harden Paymob flow

### Required fixes

* Per-tenant `iframe_id`.
* Per-tenant Paymob API key.
* Per-tenant HMAC secret.
* Webhook idempotency.
* Webhook rate limit.
* Installment payment flow.
* Bank-transfer flow.
* Receipt generation/download.

### Files to audit

```txt
server/src/routes/reservations.routes.ts
server/src/routes/payments.routes.ts
server/src/routes/webhooks.routes.ts
server/src/services/paymob.service.ts
server/src/services/paymentGateway.factory.ts
server/src/services/pdf.service.ts
client/src/features/reservation/pages/checkout-page.tsx
client/src/features/customer-dashboard/pages/payments-page.tsx
client/src/features/reservation/pages/reservation-success-page.tsx
```

### Acceptance criteria

* Tenant A and Tenant B can use different Paymob credentials.
* Webhook from Tenant A cannot confirm Tenant B payment.
* Duplicate webhook does not double-confirm reservation/payment.
* Failed HMAC is ignored safely.
* Installment “Pay Now” works.
* Bank transfer shows tenant bank details and reference number.
* Receipt PDF is available after confirmed payment.

