## 6. Add payment-state machine

Right now payment/reservation status can become messy unless every route is perfectly controlled.

### Add explicit state rules

```txt
reservation:
pending → confirmed
pending → cancelled
pending → expired
confirmed → cancelled only by admin/manager with audit reason

payment:
pending → paid
pending → overdue
overdue → paid
paid cannot go back to pending
```

### Acceptance criteria

* Invalid status transitions return 409.
* Every transition creates an activity log.
* Webhook cannot mutate already-finalized records.
* Tests cover every transition.

