## 18. Harden RLS and service-role usage

### Required

* Public RLS only exposes available public units/projects.
* Customer can read own reservations/payments/documents.
* Agent can read assigned customers/leads.
* Manager/admin can read tenant-wide data.
* Service role is used only in backend, never exposed.

### Acceptance criteria

* RLS tests prove cross-tenant reads fail.
* API tests prove Tenant A cannot access Tenant B by guessing IDs.
* Public tenant endpoint never exposes secret columns.

